de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.control

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.control.Controller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class Controller
extends Object
implements Runnable
    This class defines the general control flow of the sensorplatform.
    The class must be used as a singleton. Configured with GUICE to enforce that.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka

      • startRecordingPeriod

        public String startRecordingPeriod(long uptimeMillis,
                                   String firstname,
                                   String lastname,
                                   org.json.JSONArray sensorConfiguration,
                                   boolean isNewConfiguration)
        Start a new recording period. Multiple checks are done before doing so.
        Parameters:
        uptimeMillis - recording period time in milliseconds
        firstname - the first name of the sensorplatform user
        lastname - the last name of the sensorplatform user
        sensorConfiguration - the sensor configuration for a recording period
        isNewConfiguration - a flag which defines if a recording period is new or resumed after restart
        Returns:
        String a message for the frontend

      • run
